1. To get the Access Token and Access secret follow the link:
https://dev.twitter.com/oauth/overview/application-owner-access-tokens

To get the consumer key and consumer secret follow the steps:
Go to https://dev.twitter.com/apps/new and log in, if necessary
Supply the necessary required fields, accept the Terms Of Service, and solve the CAPTCHA.
Submit the form
Go to the API Keys tab, there you will find your Consumer key and Consumer secret keys.
Copy the consumer key (API key) and consumer secret from the screen into our application.


 
Substitute the values in the variables defined in the code.

Now to get the required R sentiment Packages:
Download the following packages from the links: 
Download the Rstem_0.4-1.tar.gz package on the desktop (or any directory of your choice)
https://cran.r-project.org/src/contrib/Archive/Rstem/

Download the sentiment_0.2.tar.gz package on the desktop (or any directory of your choice)
https://cran.r-project.org/src/contrib/Archive/sentiment/